 In the late 1940s and 1950s, 

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:13.730
 American military monsters for recordings and details of the explosion. 

00:04:13.730 --> 00:04:15.379
 How big was it exactly? 

00:04:15.379 --> 00:04:20.000
 What were the damage to the surrounding earth and whether it was due to the earthquake or the blast wave? 

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.220
 What happens if you detonate 

00:04:22.220 --> 00:04:26.860
 something with the size of an atomic bomb underground? 

